{"tid":1528073,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"罷買行動冇撚用","createTime":"2019-09-01T12:31:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T15:02:56.000Z","uid":196227,"like":25,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"5b6bbb91af4683a8e5ca783a38225da0446d496d","tid":1528073,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T12:31:41.000Z","msg":"其實set做周五至周日罷買真係冇撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n罷買除咗減低經濟目的<br />\n<br />\n另一大目的係比班商戶知道<br />\n真正比錢你賺係真香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係班藍線<br />\n<br />\n希望可以發起如五大訴求未實現<br />\n除咗生活必須品全部都唔買<br />\n必須品盡量買黃絲鋪<br />\n<br />\n我自己一個打飛機先，五大訴求未實現<br />\n我返工帶飯，所有非必須品唔會換<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申<br />\n最近對波鞋、短褲穿窿、耳機一邊爛咗⋯<br />\n好彩既係我剪撚完頭髮<br />\n但係洗頭水用完，準備做油頭毒撚<br />\n各位唔好排斥我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edada327997ac1610a2c177585f8993aea97c2bc","tid":1528073,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T12:34:16.000Z","msg":"五大訴求未實現，全港罷買呀<br />\n食飯搵黃鋪"},{"pid":"7da47bff64a8ca020ec0b3c47c3194aa4813c962","tid":1528073,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T12:36:48.000Z","msg":"希望有人陪我做呢件蠢事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81dfbd5a9b354ad8309657acfb4a2afce0bcbfb3","tid":1528073,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T12:40:30.000Z","msg":"我幫唔到係呢個運動受過傷既人<br />\n唯有用享受唔到正常生活去補償、出小小力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efe7250cda30edb92b16d0489aef44bbf4402193","tid":1528073,"uid":260793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b6bbb91af4683a8e5ca783a38225da0446d496d","tid":1528073,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T12:31:41.000Z","msg":"其實set做周五至周日罷買真係冇撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji